# Pong

# Filesystem

## filesystem stub
- file wrapper around phys memory addresses
```
struct file {
  phys_addr_t start;
  phys_addr_t end;
  uint16_t len; // bytes
  char *filename;
};
```

## Sound API
- play PCM embedded data pointed to by file wrapper
ac97.c: `void play(struct file pcm_data);`

## Graphics
- draw_rectangle(a, b, c, d);
- clear_screen();
- implement the double pointer method
`render()` - swap buffers

## Keyboard API

- poll for key status (pressed, not pressed)
- pseudo mask certain key events from driver (similar to on key event listener in (js?))

`int is_key_pressed(int scan_code /* or some enum to map this */);`

`void addListener(int maskFilter, ())`
